{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"24aca622-6f7f-4d6a-84ce-83f2614a40a2","content":"In modern MSTest (v3.8+), use **constructor injection** for `TestContext` and combine it with `[ClassInitialize]` / `[TestInitialize]` for async setup. Here's the recommended pattern:\n\n```csharp\n[TestClass]\npublic class MyTests\n{\n    public TestContext TestContext { get; }\n\n    // Constructor injection for TestContext (MSTest 3.6+)\n    public MyTests(TestContext testContext)\n    {\n        TestContext = testContext;\n        // Synchronous init here (e.g., create objects, set fields)\n    }\n\n    [ClassInitialize]\n    public static async Task ClassSetup(TestContext context)\n    {\n        // One-time async setup (e.g., start test server, seed DB)\n        await Task.CompletedTask;\n    }\n\n    [TestInitialize]\n    public async Task TestSetup()\n    {\n        // Per-test async setup (e.g., reset state)\n        await Task.CompletedTask;\n    }\n\n    [TestMethod]\n    public void SampleTest()\n    {\n        Assert.IsNotNull(TestContext);\n    }\n\n    [ClassCleanup]\n    public static async Task ClassTeardown()\n    {\n        // One-time async cleanup\n        await Task.CompletedTask;\n    }\n\n    [TestCleanup]\n    public async Task TestTeardown()\n    {\n        // Per-test async cleanup\n        await Task.CompletedTask;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n\n- **Constructor** — receives `TestContext` via DI; use for synchronous setup. A new instance is created per test.\n- **`[ClassInitialize]`** — `static async Task`, runs once per class; use for expensive async setup.\n- **`[TestInitialize]`** — `async Task`, runs before each test; use for per-test async setup.\n- Constructor injection for `TestContext` requires **MSTest ≥ 3.6**. Your project (3.8.2) supports it.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"ba6e3f5a-8ff6-4185-b883-26bfa785830b","outputTokens":493,"requestId":"6039:1287AC:25B7E0D:2854F41:6A0311E5"},"id":"dffa86b0-99f8-4951-b759-55847ab7bc54","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:41:40.110Z","parentId":"35016e92-5500-48b8-872a-4787d20a7db5"}
